import math
n = int(input())
while n:
    n -= 1
    a = [int(x) for x in input().split()]
    num = a[3] - a[5]
    dno = a[5] - a[1]
    if num < 0 or dno < 0:
        print('NO')
        continue
    g = math.gcd(num, dno)
    num /= g
    dno /= g
    total_parts = num + dno
    volume_of_part = a[4] / total_parts
    if volume_of_part * num > a[0]:
        print('NO')
        continue
    if volume_of_part * dno > a[2]:
        print('NO')
        continue
    print('YES')
